Axiom has moved to gcl-2.6.2 (pre-release) on savannah.
This will have no impact on anything. 

You can download the lastest sources with:

export CVS_RSH=ssh
cvs -z3 -d:ext:anoncvs@savannah.nongnu.org:/cvsroot/axiom co axiom

Tim



