Hi Mike,

Right, it works with Axiom 2.3. (Since I have set ALDORROOT and 
AXIOMXLROOT to point to the new aldor compiler (not the one which comes 
with Axiom 2.3), I had to make a link
   ln -s aldor.conf axiomxl.conf
in $ALDORROOT/include.

Unfortunately, I don't know how to force a backtrace.

Is OpenAxiom relying on the environment variable ALDORROOT or AXIOMXLROOT?

Ralf

